room.challenge_info: {"cid":"1578133340879901","cha_name":"丁程鑫","desc":"丁程鑫，2002年2月24日出生于四川省资阳市安岳县，中国内地流行乐男歌手、影视演员，男子演唱组合时代少年团成员。\n2013年，在TF家族自制综艺《TF少年GO》中首次走进大众视野 。2015年，参加录制TF家族自制综艺《星期五练习生》。2016年，参演科幻校园网剧《超少年密码》 和青春励志剧《旋风少女第二季》 。2017年4月，参加录制湖南卫视文化节目《中华文明之美》；7月，参演青春励志剧《我们的少年时代》；11月，首登湖南卫视综艺节目《快乐大本营》。2018年，参演奇幻校园网剧《念念》和青春励志剧《甜蜜暴击》。2019年2月，参加录制的综艺《台风少年行》播出；3月，参加录制央视文化音乐节目《经典咏流传》第二季。2020年1月，参加录制的综艺《少年梦游记》播出。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1578133340879901","author":{"uid":"6796248446","short_id":"52","nickname":"抖音小助手","gender":1,"signature":"本宝宝暂时还没想到个性签名","avatar_larger":{"uri":"1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":true,"constellation":10,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_verify":"","unique_id":"douyin","bind_phone":"","special_lock":0,"need_recommend":0,"is_binded_weibo":false,"weibo_name":"","weibo_schema":"","weibo_url":"","story_open":false,"story_count":0,"has_facebook_token":false,"has_twitter_token":false,"fb_expire_time":0,"tw_expire_time":0,"has_youtube_token":false,"youtube_expire_time":0,"room_id":0,"li
